title: No. 5 Hokies even series with No. 7 Louisville - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 5 Hokies even series with No. 7 Louisville  VT hokiesports.com
description: Staked an early lead by Gavin Cross hitting his 12th home run of the season on Saturday, the No. 5 Virginia Tech baseball team held off No. 7 Louisville, 4-3, to even the teams' top-10 ACC series at English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park.
